DESCRIPTION >
    Per-user first API activity time, maintained incrementally from
    generation_event. Used by kpi_activations so the endpoint does not compute
    min(start_time) across the raw generation_event table on every dashboard
    request.

TOKEN "tinybird_read" READ

SCHEMA >
    `user_id` String,
    `first_activity_time` AggregateFunction(min, DateTime)

ENGINE AggregatingMergeTree
ENGINE_SORTING_KEY user_id
